My sister in law @vanesa.belle helped me out with this video to compare 🌸pink🌸 & 🍑peach🍑 corrector & powder under the eyes! 
I have a more pink skin tone than her and so assumed pink would be the way to go… however I noticed the peach actually colour corrected so so much better even on my pale skin! For her both looked good to me!! 

Takeaways:
We felt 🍑peach did better to counteract blue eye bags, and looked more natural especially on her.
But 🌸pink had such a nice brightening effect and in the end we preferred it for our Friday night glam! 

What do you guys think?
